<ab facs="#facs_284_r2l6">Bertlein von Swangöw <expan>gebrud<ex>er</ex></expan> . <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> . <expan>geg<ex>en</ex></expan> vns fürge = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_284_r2l7"><expan>nom<ex>m</ex>en</expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> . von ein <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan> . f . ʒeſels <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / Darauf vns eẅr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_284_r2l8"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> Ernſts gnade <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> geſagt hat daʒ ſıch eẅr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_284_r2l9"><expan>beıd<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> <expan>gnedıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> in den <expan>ſache<ex>n</ex></expan> beweıſet habe . des wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_284_r2l10"><expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> mıt fleıſſ danken . Nu mag eẅr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> . von dem <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_284_r2l11"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd auch in den <expan>ſchrıfte<ex>n</ex></expan> dıe wır ~ den von Swangöw </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_284_r2l12">vormals <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> getan <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> . wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>m</ex>en</expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> daʒ wır <expan>ſölıch<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
