<ab facs="#facs_284_r2l14">niht ʒu ſchıken vnd Jm auch rechtes von den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> bey vns ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_284_r2l15">helffen <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıchen</expan> . Völlıklıch <expan>gebotte<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd nıe <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſagt</expan> <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> . Dar - </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_284_r2l16">umb <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅr <expan>fürſtenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade dıenſtlıch . dıe <expan>obgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_284_r2l17">Swangöw ʒu <expan>vnt<ex>er</ex>weıſen</expan> . ſıch des <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>enteẅſſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
