<ab facs="#facs_284_r2l20">ye niht geſein daʒ denn eẅr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> . <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> von Swangöw vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_284_r2l21">vns / <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>gerawme<ex>n</ex></expan> tag für eẅr gnade <expan>ſecʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>beſchaıd<ex>en</ex></expan> . Da - </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_284_r2l22">hin wır <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> ſchıken <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> glimpf vor <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_284_r2l23"><expan>fürſtenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu ercʒeln / daʒ wır hoffen bey gelimpf ʒu beſteen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_284_r2l24">Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dıenſt vnd wolgefallen etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_284_r2l25"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>ſ<ex>upra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_284" id="141r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>czog</expan> Ernsten und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan>
<expan>Wilhelm<ex>m</ex></expan>, <expan>gebrüd<ex>er</ex>n</expan> von
                        Peyern etc.</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnedigen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, als wir
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> Göldlein nehst zu
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> gesandt <expan>hette<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        von des handels <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, den in
                            <expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> und
                        Bertlein von Swangöw, <expan>gebrud<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>geg<ex>en</ex></expan> uns <expan>fürgenom<ex>m</ex>en</expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, von ein <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan>
<expan>F<ex>riedrich</ex></expan> Zesels <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                        darauf uns ewr <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan> Ernsts gnade
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> gesagt hat, daz sich ewr
                                <expan>beid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> in den <expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        beweiset habe, des wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> mit fleiss danken. Nu mag ewr
                                <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> von dem
                                <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> und auch in den
                            <expan>schrifte<ex>n</ex></expan>, die wir den von Swangöw vormals
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> getan <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                        wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>m</ex>en</expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz wir <expan>sölich<ex>er</ex></expan> sach
                        und sprüche, die im der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>F<ex>riedrich</ex></expan> Zesel fürnymbt, in
                            <expan>sund<ex>er</ex>heit</expan> niht zu schiken und im auch rechtes
                        von den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> bey uns zu helffen
                                <expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lichen</expan> völliklich
                                <expan>gebotte<ex>n</ex></expan> und nie
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>sagt</expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>. Darumb <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr
                                <expan>fürstenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade dienstlich, die
                                <expan>obgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> von Swangöw zu
                                <expan>unt<ex>er</ex>weisen</expan>, sich des
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urgers</ex></expan> zu <expan>entewss<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und
                        uns sprüche von <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> zu <expan>v<ex>er</ex>tragen</expan> und zu
                                <expan>erlass<ex>en</ex></expan>, wan wir mit in niht
                                <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> zu <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> denn guts; möcht <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        des ye niht gesein, daz denn ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan> von Swangöw und uns
                            <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>gerawme<ex>n</ex></expan> tag für ewr gnade
                            <expan>secze<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>beschaid<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                        dahin wir <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> schiken <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> glimpf vor
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> zu erczeln, daz wir hoffen bey gelimpf zu
                        besteen. Denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dienst und wolgefallen etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
